name: LifeBankChain
description: LBC aims to establish a secure storage application platform for gene and stem cell data collaboration based on individual and institutional nodes, scalable cross chain services. The platform product service layer abstracts all typical gene and stem cell blockchain applications, providing complete functionality and implementation framework for typical applications. Purchase all services provided on LBC through LBCToken, including testing, treatment, and customized gene and stem cell products, as well as related benefits.
